# Fiber_photometry_video_sync_tag_app_V1

A MATLAB App Designer tool for **time-locked review of fiber-photometry signals and behavior video**, with per-ROI processing (470/410 correction, ΔF/F%), digital marker/trigger overlays, and a lightweight behavior-tagging workflow that exports to Excel.

